Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.98,0:20:33.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,「たすけてよ」こぼれ落ちる　言葉は灰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.11,0:20:35.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,私をとめて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.04,0:20:52.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,まただ　嫉跖と憧憬と独占欲で
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.30,0:20:55.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,体が千切れそうになる
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.43,0:21:01.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,つぶれるよ　みてごらん
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.18,0:21:04.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,ぐちゃぐちゃだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.10,0:21:09.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,例えば　約束ち
